    "description": "Almado, Inc. engages in the planning, development, and sale of cosmetics and supplements in Japan. The company offers skin care products, including serum; serum for whitening; moisturizing eggshell membrane; wrinkle-reducing, moisturizing, firmness, and glow; facial cleansing and makeup removal with electrolyzed water; brightening lotion and cream; and hyaluronic acid spicules products. It offers beauty, beauty drink, and hair growth supplement products. In addition, it is involved in the contract manufacturing activities. The company markets its products under the Ode and CELLULA brands. It sells its products to TV shopping channels, OME manufacturing companies, drug stores, hairdressers, and mail order companies, as well as operates an e-commerce website. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
